    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factors achieving levels below required thresholds, the assessment team determined that the CFD hemolysis predictions are sufficiently credible for the VAD COU given the conservative uncertainty bounds established by Monte Carlo UQ. Several factors lack formal acceptanceCriteria documentation; this package is flagged as adversarial to test W-AR-01 detection.",
